  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's a certain group in Teaneck, New Jersey, that-- they are from the [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Chabad ?] movement.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I'm more than proud, they gave me so much comfort during the days when I needed, that I don't think that one should forget such people existence.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the support, the moral support, and the actual-- actual support that they provided in-- in the moments that one felt that he is down on this earth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have to mention that last year I had the unfortunate encounter of being hit as, on a sidewalk by a car as a pedestrian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And with the help of these people who were coming in [? trunks ?] to visit me in the hospital and bring me all kinds of goodies, I somehow got myself together that, to a point that I can just talk about it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And like Jewish people say, this is a day of a miracle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I hope that this new Jewish year will provide us with a better outlook on, not only for us, but like they say Hebrew, [SPEAKING HEBREW], of all the Jewish nation of Israel, to encounter a better life and perhaps a peace that they are pray-- with we are praying so much about it, will finally come to the a point that people will live alongside of with one another and turn their weapons into plows of Joshua prediction for a better life upon this earth.",
      "word_count": 87
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There are many atrocities in this world that still exist and perhaps under cover.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there where the United Nation should really do something about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it turned into a powerful money-collecting place, not paying sufficient amount of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
